  "text_preview": "\"play-cards\" ASL American Sign Language ASL University ► play-cards PLAY-CARDS: In general I just sign PLAY and fingerspell C-A-R-D-S. But you can also show this concept by showing the dealing of cards: As I mentioned, I just spell the concept of \"cards\" but you can indicate an individual card by showing the shape of the card: Also see the CHECK page. ASL University ► You can learn American Sign Language (ASL) online at American Sign Language University ™ ASL resources by Lifeprint.com © Dr. William Vicars American Sign Language University ™ ASL resources by Lifeprint.com © Dr. William Vicars You can learn American Sign Language (ASL) online at American Sign Language University ™ ASL resources by Lifeprint.com © Dr. William Vicars"
